SMART_CALCULATOR

Type your expression like in your math's notebook! For example: (123 - 52)/18 - 6
Type "/exit" to terminate the program.
Type "/help" to get more information about this app.
You can assign value to variable, type your variable name and next use "=" operator and your value to assign it.
Apps supports operations like: addition "+", multiplication "*", subtraction "-", division "/", powers "^" and calculations in parentheses "()".
Name of the variable only can have letters (case sensitive) and underscore ("_").
Type "/rules" to get more information about variables naming rules.
If you want to see your previous inputs, type "/history".
If you want to see every variable you put in the program, type "/variables".

